#: ../../T/tenured-graduate-student.rst:5
msgid "tenured graduate student"
msgstr "tenured graduate student"

#: ../../T/tenured-graduate-student.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../T/tenured-graduate-student.rst:9
msgid ""
"One who has been in graduate school for 10 years (the usual maximum is 5 or "
"6): a ‘ten-yeared’ student (get it?). Actually, this term may be used of any"
" grad student beginning in his seventh year. Students don't really get "
"tenure, of course, the way professors do, but a tenth-year graduate student "
"has probably been around the university longer than any untenured professor."
msgstr ""
"大学院に10年いる者(通常の上限は5年か6年):‘ten-"
"yeared’学生(分かるかい?)。実際には、この用語は7年目に入ったあらゆる大学院生に使われることがある。もちろん学生は、教授がそうするようには本当にtenure(終身在職権)を得るわけではないが、10年目の大学院生はおそらく、終身在職権のないどの教授よりも長く大学にいたことになる。"
